# CODEOWNERS

# EdenCORP Standards Repository — CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to each part
# of this repository. Reviewers are automatically requested when a PR
# modifies files matching their pattern.
#
# Format: <pattern> <owner> [<owner> ...]
# Owners can be GitHub teams or individual usernames.
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for all files not explicitly matched below.
# Leadership and platform team review all changes.
*                                   @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform

# Core standards documents require leadership sign-off.
README.md                           @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                  @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform
CONTRIBUTING.md                     @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform
SECURITY.md                         @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform

# Architecture and development standards — platform team owns these.
ARCHITECTURE.md                     @edencorp/platform @edencorp/leadership
DEVELOPMENT.md                      @edencorp/platform
INFRASTRUCTURE.md                   @edencorp/platform
BRANCHING_STRATEGY.md               @edencorp/platform
COMMIT_CONVENTIONS.md               @edencorp/platform
VERSIONING.md                       @edencorp/platform

# AI engineering standards — prism team (AI) co-owns with platform.
AI_ENGINEERING.md                   @edencorp/prism @edencorp/platform @edencorp/leadership

# Testing and quality standards.
TESTING.md                          @edencorp/platform

# Process documents.
REVIEW_PROCESS.md                   @edencorp/platform @edencorp/leadership
INCIDENT_RESPONSE.md                @edencorp/platform @edencorp/leadership
DOCUMENTATION.md                    @edencorp/platform

# Templates — platform team maintains these.
templates/                          @edencorp/platform

# CODEOWNERS itself requires leadership sign-off.
CODEOWNERS                          @edencorp/leadership @edencorp/platform
